\u4fdd\u5b9a) after 1949\n|-\n|[[Hunan]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u6e56\u5357}}</span>||H\u00fan\u00e1n\n|<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u6e58}}</span>||Xi\u0101ng\n|[[Changsha]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u9577\u6c99}}</span>||Ch\u00e1ngsh\u0101||\n|-\n|[[Hubei|Hupeh]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u6e56\u5317}}</span>||H\u00fab\u011bi\n|<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u9102}}</span>||\u00c8\n|[[Wuchang, Hubei|Wuchang]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u6b66\u660c}}</span>||W\u01d4ch\u0101ng||\n|-\n|[[Xing'an Province|Hsingan]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u8208\u5b89}}</span>||X\u012bng'\u0101n\n|<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u8208}}</span>||X\u012bng\n|[[Hulunbuir|Hailar]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u6d77\u62c9\u723e}}</span>|| H\u01ceil\u0101'\u011br\n|1947 created from [[Manchukuo]] (originally part of Heilungkiang)<br>Hailar was renamed to [[Hulunbuir]] (\u547c\u502b\u8c9d\u723e) after 1949\n|-\n|[[Rehe Province|Jehol]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u71b1\u6cb3}}</span>||R\u00e8h\u00e9\n|<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u71b1}}</span>||R\u00e8\n|[[Chengde|Chengteh]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u627f\u5fb7}}</span>||Ch\u00e9ngd\u00e9\n|1928 reformed from a special administrative region, 1945 recreated from [[Manchukuo]]\n|-\n|[[Gansu|Kansu]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u7518\u8085}}</span>||G\u0101ns\u00f9\n|<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u96b4}}</span>||L\u01d2ng\n|[[Lanzhou|Lanchow]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u862d\u5dde}}</span>||L\u00e1nzh\u014du||\n|-\n|[[Jiangxi|Kiangsi]]||<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u6c5f\u897f}}</span>||Ji\u0101ngx\u012b\n|<span style=\"font-size:125%;\">{{lang|zh-hant|\u8d1b}}</span>||G\u00e0n\n|[[Nanchang]]||<span style=\"font-siz